node.text:
Staying fit and maintaining my muscle mass during these hard times👊🏻 All you need for this workout is a resistance tube and a mini band. 
Perform 3 rounds of each circuit before moving on to the next:

1a: one arm shoulder press - 15 reps ea
1b: biceps curl - 15 reps slow descent
1c: rows - 15 reps

2a: pull down - 15 reps
2b: chest press - 15 reps
2c: one legged RDL - 15 reps ea

3a: slow descent squats - 15 reps
3b: triceps overhead - 15 reps
3c: narrow push ups - 15 reps

node.text:
Who are these two young guys? 
On set of Universal Solider 30 years ago. @jcvd

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on September 10, 2021 tagging @emmakrokdal. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and flower.

node.text: One last night on London Town before starting Aquaman 2. Dinner at Annabel’s of course.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Came across this photo of the late Brandon Lee in front of the Warners billboard of ‘Showdown in Little Tokyo’ almost 30 years ago. Brandon was a great guy and a great actor. He is very much missed. 🙏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and nature.

node.text: The calm before the storm. Taking some chilled time off before heading to London for Aquaman 2. 👊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 25, 2021. May be an image of 11 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: A long awaited family luncheon in Stockholm. Just another group of short Scandinavians…

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on August 21, 2021 tagging @emmakrokdal. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting and sky.

node.text: Take it easy. No more photos from Stockholm!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: With my brother Johan at the Uppsala Cathedral in Sweden. Great to see him after over a year of travel restrictions. Feels good!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.
Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.
Photo by Dolph Lundgren on August 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: The Olympics is such a great event infusing the whole world with positive energy, which is always needed. 🙏🙏 I did a picture in the early 90’s called ‘Pentathlon’, where I played an East-German pentathlete who defects to the US during the Gsm s. Hence, the double layered uniforms. By the time the film was released, the Berlin Wall had fallen and East-Germany had soon ceased to exist.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Ten years ago, we started shooting ‘Expendables 2’. Wonder what Gunner’s been up to lately? 👊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Just another day at the office!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on July 10, 2021 tagging @hiramamurray, and @kellanlutz. May be an image of 3 people and outdoors.

node.text: With some of my brothers in arms on the set of ‘Come Out Fighting’. A great story focusing on one of the first ‘colored units’ in the US Army during WW 2, the 761st Tank Battalion, which first saw action in France in 1944.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on July 10, 2021 tagging @hiramamurray, and @kellanlutz. May be an image of 3 people and outdoors.
Photo by Dolph Lundgren on July 10, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and outdoors.
